  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess prevalence of gastrooesophageal reflux during
      childhood and teenage years in France and to describe patients'symptoms and gastrooesophageal
      reflux management
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
